个早餐 **如果回来自动化程序没拉闸，可能送到 300 位**\r\n\r\n ![]( https://i.imgur.com/cofYFwP.png) \r\n\r\n\r\n## 微信群\r\n\r\n ![]( https://i.imgur.com/nCgOV12.png) \r\n\r\n\r\n## 一起建设我们的 VibeCoding 社区\r\n\r\n* 欢迎有志之士加入我们的 VibeCoding 社区，我们正在招募成员一起建设 VibeCoding 社区\r\n\r\n[https://bbs.vibe-coding.sh]( https://bbs.vibe-coding.sh)", "content_rendered": "<p>在 V 站宣传有一段时间了，积累不了少客户，有些朋友用的不开心走了，有的朋友退款了，但是老板还在，老板又回来给 v 友发福利了</p>\n<p>claude-free 渠道 限时开启，避免滥用，只要 5 分一刀</p>\n<p><strong>官网地址</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://terminal.pub/register\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://terminal.pub/register</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>充值 1 人民币=1 美金, 套餐可以 0.9 人民币=1 美金</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>活动规则</h2>\n<p>老规矩，回帖发自己 id 每个人送 10 刀，仅限前 150 位\n<img alt=\"图片\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0oWfkP0.png\"/></p>\n<p>我去吃个早餐 <strong>如果回来自动化程序没拉闸，可能送到 300 位</strong></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cofYFwP.png\"/> </p>\n<h2>微信群</h2>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nCgOV12.png\"/> </p>\n<h2>一起建设我们的 VibeCoding 社区</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>欢迎有志之士加入我们的 VibeCoding 社区，我们正在招募成员一起建设 VibeCoding 社区</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://bbs.vibe-coding.sh\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://bbs.vibe-coding.sh</a></p>\n", "last_modified": 1777334753, "replies": 237, "id": 1208985}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/ccb0/9896/755_large.png?m=1402729057", "name": "libido", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/ccb0/9896/755_normal.png?m=1402729057", "title": "情感问题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/libido", "topics": 1743, "footer": "", "header": "有些事情不必一直憋在心里，说出来让大家听听，然后一起想办法吧。", "title_alternative": "Libido", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/ccb0/9896/755_mini.png?m=1402729057", "stars": 902, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 755, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 731383, "username": "bearbest", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/bearbest", "website": "https://bear.best", "twitter": "xbearbest", "psn": "", "github": "gBearBest", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/01d9/815f/731383_mini.png?m=1770105400", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/01d9/815f/731383_normal.png?m=1770105400", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/01d9/815f/731383_large.png?m=1770105400", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/01d9/815f/731383_xlarge.png?m=1770105400", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/01d9/815f/731383_xxlarge.png?m=1770105400", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/01d9/815f/731383_xxxlarge.png?m=1770105400", "created": 1737125319, "last_modified": 1770105400, "pro": 1777353550}, "last_reply_by": "happinessnch", "last_touched": 1777353024, "title": "对象躺得太平了怎么办？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1208836", "created": 1777273231, "deleted": 0, "content": "工作上八九年没什么变化。\r\n\r\n生活上没什么兴趣爱好。\r\n\r\n每天下班或是周末就是躺着刷视频看直播玩游戏。\r\n\r\n好像完全没有努力让两个人的生活变得更好的想法，过一天算一天，每天得过且过。\r\n\r\n两人也聊过相关话题，聊得时候发现自己都清楚这些问题，但是聊完之后就像从来没聊过一样……\r\n\r\n我想一起培养点两个人共同的兴趣爱好，比如游泳、潜水、甚至旅游，都没兴趣。\r\n\r\n出去玩也喜欢躺在酒店里……\r\n\r\n问：有什么感兴趣的吗？答曰：我也不知道对啥感兴趣\r\n\r\n有什么办法改善吗？我们的感情还是很好的，就是感觉有点玩不到一起去。\r\n\r\n不想变成完成任务的队友搭子，更希望是彼此搀扶前进的爱人。🙏", "content_rendered": "工作上八九年没什么变化。<br /><br />生活上没什么兴趣爱好。<br /><br />每天下班或是周末就是躺着刷视频看直播玩游戏。<br /><br />好像完全没有努力让两个人的生活变得更好的想法，过一天算一天，每天得过且过。<br /><br />两人也聊过相关话题，聊得时候发现自己都清楚这些问题，但是聊完之后就像从来没聊过一样……<br /><br />我想一起培养点两个人共同的兴趣爱好，比如游泳、潜水、甚至旅游，都没兴趣。<br /><br />出去玩也喜欢躺在酒店里……<br /><br />问：有什么感兴趣的吗？答曰：我也不知道对啥感兴趣<br /><br />有什么办法改善吗？我们的感情还是很好的，就是感觉有点玩不到一起去。<br /><br />不想变成完成任务的队友搭子，更希望是彼此搀扶前进的爱人。🙏", "last_modified": 1777273256, "replies": 155, "id": 1208836}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_large.png?m=1650127482", "name": "shanghai", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_normal.png?m=1650127482", "title": "上海", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/shanghai", "topics": 3966, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Shanghai", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_mini.png?m=1650127482", "stars": 2570, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 18, "parent_node_name": "cn"}, "member": {"id": 604449, "username": "gotOwt", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/gotOwt", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/aeb0/c0ec/604449_mini.png?m=1775634004", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/aeb0/c0ec/604449_normal.png?m=1775634004", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/aeb0/c0ec/604449_large.png?m=1775634004", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/aeb0/c0ec/604449_xlarge.png?m=1775634004", "created": 1669943889, "last_modified": 1775634004, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "quijote", "last_touched": 1777353635, "title": "有人开过塔斯汀吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1208994", "created": 1777338271, "deleted": 0, "content": "坐标上海，发现附近 4km 内没有塔斯汀店。。\r\n感觉是个机遇，这边人很多。。\r\n有说法吗？\r\n---\r\n一直都是程序员，没干过餐饮。。\r\n想看看大家的想法。", "content_rendered": "坐标上海，发现附近 4km 内没有塔斯汀店。。<br />感觉是个机遇，这边人很多。。<br />有说法吗？<br />---<br />一直都是程序员，没干过餐饮。。<br />想看看大家的想法。", "last_modified": 1777342388, "replies": 98, "id": 1208994}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1768280127", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1768280127", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 23139, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1768280127", "stars": 3660, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 584347, "username": "terry204